Puppet module: wordpress

# Written by Tom McGonagle #
# mcgonagle@gmail.com
# Google Voice (617)229-5185
# http://www.puppetll.com


DESCRIPTION:
This module installs and manages wordpress software
Standard and extended classes are available.
Decide and customize how you want to define configation files: static files, templates, infile modifications...


USAGE:
# Standard Classes 
include wordpress              # Install and run wordpress with standard configurations.
include wordpress::disable     # Disable wordpress service.
include wordpress::disableboot # Disable wordpress service at boot time, but don't stop if it's running.
include wordpress::absent      # Remove wordpress package.

DEPENDENCIES:
